&lt;h3&gt;int( ) and str( ):&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;int( ): 將&lt;span style="background-color: #ffff00"&gt;有字串的數字&lt;/span&gt;轉為整數,例如: int('123') = 123,而不是'123',int(12.123) = 12,int(12.123+1) = 13
